Hamid Termina

Hamid Termina (born January 5, 1977) is a Moroccan football player. As of February 2009, he plays for Safa Sporting Club. He made his Bundesliga debut for FC Energie Cottbus on August 19, 2001 when he started in a game against Hertha BSC Berlin.

