The title refers to the . "Tori Uta" was previously released as "" on "Zoundtrack" by Ukawanimation!.
"Fukurou: 13 Japanese Birds Pt. 2".
The title refers to the . "Gorosukehoukou" and "Noritsukehousei" are Japanese onomatopoeia for the sounds of owls.
